Use Joystick to move: left, right, jump. Press FIRE.
Player 1 press FIRE to hit The Eraser.
Hit the Eraser until the Bits of Life reach 0.
Player 2 Position yourself on the YELLOW bitblock. Press FIRE to convert.
Convert over 50% of the YELLOW bitblocks before the Bits of Life reach 0. 
Head right and press FIRE to reavel each ITEM and its effect. 
GREEN Gem: Freezes the Eraser for a set amount of time.
ORANGE Gem: Doubles the damage if The Eraser gets hit.
RED Potion: Red picks up, Eraser loses 1Bit. Blue picks up, Eraser gains 1Bit.
BLUE Potion: If Blue picks up SPEED BOOST. If Red picks up SLOW DOWN.






















































































































































































































































